Sunday 16 Sep

4:15PM

Henning Wehn

Rosie Jones

Tom Lucy

Kiri Pritchard-Mclean

Self styled German Comedy Ambassador Henning Wehn headlines a huge afternoon at Greenwich Comedy Festival. Expect a hit packed set from the Would I Lie To You Star -packed full of inimitable teutonic jolliness.

Wehn wraps his vowels around the issues of immigration and identity

The Times
Joining Henning is a superb lineup including a special guest to be announced, mischievous 8 Out Of 10 Cats star Rosie Jones, fast-rising Stand Up Central star Tom Lucy and the magnificently funny Kiri Pritchard-Mclean as host.
